description: "Serious Moonlight Tour" 1983...Bowie's biggest tour excursion up to this point.  The "Let's Dance" album was a huge success, and this set list, in true order, is very eclectic considering how MTV/pop Bowie's persona was in 1983...a great listen for those who are sick of greatest hits packages.
name: David Bowie -Set List 7/30/1983 Joe Louis Arena, Detroit, MI

album.name: The Rise and Fall of Ziggy Stardust and the Spiders from Mars (2012 Remaster)

track.name: White Light / White Heat - Live '83, 2018 Remaster
